Proposed caption: A simple page-by-page annotation-editor example for the
French segment ``« Je t'aime », dit-il.'' The editor tokenises the French
guillemets and punctuation as separate items, displays an English translation,
and presents token, MWE, lemma, POS and gloss columns with a `Save this
segment' control.
